Are You Smart enough? Do you know your flags?
GuiDE TO the game :
Match the flags, test your memory.

Is your memory fast enough?
Basically, they will be a start button for you to begin the game.
Once you begin they will be a score board for every game completed.

After selecting you answer, the cards shift left and a new card is pulled 
from the pile on the right. The card that was previously face up on the right is now face 
down in the middle. And the card previously in the middle is now on the left. 
You need to determine if the newly pulled card matches the card now on the left.
Or it can be anywhere on the game once refresh, they will be no way to cheat and i 
will not guide you to cheat.





